<node TEXT="System/Application classloader" ID="ID_1145862450" CREATED="1553839133478" MODIFIED="1553839226411"><richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      This is the child classloader of Extension classloader. It loads the classfiles from classpath. By default, classpath is set to current directory. You can change the classpath using &quot;-cp&quot; or &quot;-classpath&quot; switch. It is also known as Application classloader.
    </p>
