<node TEXT="LinkedHashSet" ID="ID_94183666" CREATED="1552025120939" MODIFIED="1554569079075"><richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      extends Hash set
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;</font><a class="APILink" target="_blank" href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/LinkedHashSet.html" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(58, 135, 207); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font color="rgb(58, 135, 207)" face="Monaco, Courier, Courier New" size="12.8px"><code style="font-family: Monaco, Courier, Courier New">LinkedHashSet</code></font></a><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">, which is implemented as a hash table with a linked list running through it, orders its elements based on the order in which they were inserted into the set (insertion-order).&#160;</font><code style="font-family: Monaco, Courier, Courier New; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12.8px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font face="Monaco, Courier, Courier New" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" size="12.8px">LinkedHashSet</font></code><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;spares its clients from the unspecified, generally chaotic ordering provided by&#160;</font><code style="font-family: Monaco, Courier, Courier New; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12.8px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"><font face="Monaco, Courier, Courier New" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" size="12.8px">HashSet</font></code><font color="rgb(0, 0, 0)" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&#160;at a cost that is only slightly higher. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px">Note that insertion order is</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px"><i style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">not</i></font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px">affected if an element is</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px"><i style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">re-inserted</i>into the set.</font><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160; </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">It can be used to produce a copy of a set that has the same order as the original, regardless of the original set's implementation: </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;void foo(Set s) { </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Set copy = new LinkedHashSet(s); </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;... </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif">&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;} </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px">A linked hash set has two parameters that affect its performance:</font></span><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px"><span>&#160;</span><i style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">initial capacity</i><span>&#160;</span><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">and</span><span>&#160;</span><i style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">load factor</i><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none">. They are defined precisely as for</span><span>&#160;</span></font><tt style="font-family: DejaVu Sans Mono, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 4px; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><font face="DejaVu Sans Mono, monospace" size="14px" color="rgb(71, 71, 71)">HashSet</font></tt><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px">. Note, however, that the penalty for choosing an excessively high value for initial capacity is less severe for this class than for</font></span><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px"><span>&#160;</span></font><tt style="font-family: DejaVu Sans Mono, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding-top: 4px; margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><font face="DejaVu Sans Mono, monospace" size="14px" color="rgb(71, 71, 71)">HashSet</font></tt><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-family: DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="rgb(71, 71, 71)" face="DejaVu Serif, Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="14px">, as iteration times for this class are unaffected by capacity.</font></span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>

</richcontent>
